WISE is LIVE NOW! WISE will REFUND up to 70% of your gas fees for the first 20,000 ETH sent to the contract (current balance: 23,081 ETH)

WISE Token Reservations

The launch of the WISE contract will kick off an initial 50 day phase during which users can reserve tokens by creating a liquidity pool from ETH contributions.
